Kickboxers of Limpopo Province Sport Karate/Kickboxing Club graded to their next belts during a grading session at the club in Polo­kwane recently.
Coach Nico Myburgh indicated that it was a tough grading and members had to show extreme talent and skills in order to advance to the next belt.
Story: RC Myburgh
>>rc.observer@gmail.com
The junior kickboxers who graded are in front Zayden Vogel, Christene Botha and Tristin-Blake Raath. At the back are Faith Wolfaardt, Zuan Roux, Frank Roux, Suné Booysen, Alex Vogel and Carol-Ann Botha.